Designed for children ages 3-12 years old, your free Kid Crew membership includes monthly events, prizes, goody bags, perks for parents and more!
To Enroll
Click Here
Membership cards can be picked up  in the Mall Management Offices between 9:00am-5:00pm, Monday through Friday.
Parent/Guardian must accompany child when picking up membership card. Child must be present to receive membership card.
KID CREW DISCOUNTS
(Membership card and named child must be presented at the time of purchase to receive discount)
